commit message:
sloan_singleband tree: Correct examples counts and add icons.

See https://github.com/zooniverse/Galaxy-Zoo/pull/198#issuecomment-102073728

sloan_singleband tree: Correct the bulge_dominant answer.

This was caused by an incorrect closing quote in the .coffeescript file.
See https://github.com/zooniverse/Galaxy-Zoo/pull/198#issuecomment-102167639

sloan_singleband tree: Remove newline from help text.

These were added when I used Android Studio's reformatter. I usually
use xmllint.

decision trees: Correct 'a image' typos.

See https://github.com/zooniverse/Galaxy-Zoo/pull/195
IconsCacheTest: Add a message to an assert.

ExampleViewer: Take and try an alternative URL.

* DecisionTree: Add getExampleIconNameWithCommonMistake(). Often the - after
the survey group name, before the question number, is a _ in the example
file name. That breaks the web UI's ability to show full example images too.
But this lets us try those URLs instead of waiting for the filenames
to be corrected on the server.
* ExampleViewerActivity, ExampleViewerFragment: Take an alternative URI and
try it if the first one failed.
* QuestionHelpFragment: Pass the alternative URL.

See https://github.com/zooniverse/Galaxy-Zoo/pull/198
IconsCacheTest: Added some commented-out code to fall back to the alternative URL.
